To design, implement, and evaluate a Decentralized Zero Trust Network Access system
that provides resilient, tamper-proof authentication and AI-enhanced behavioral security
for IoT-enabled smart classroom networks, operating effectively in resource-constrained
educational environments without dependency on cloud authentication infrastructure.
