2.5.2 Integration Testing
Integration testing validates end-to-end behavior across the combined Mininet-Ryu-
Blockchain-TensorFlow Lite stack. A series of test scenarios exercises the complete
authentication flow from device packet arrival through blockchain query to flow rule
installation or denial, verifying that the three-component pipeline operates correctly under
realistic timing conditions. Additional integration tests validate behavior during component
failure conditions: blockchain server unavailability (Ryu should default to deny), AI
detector process crash (system should continue operating with authentication-only
security), and high-concurrency device connection bursts (50 simultaneous Packet-In
events).
2.5.3 Security Penetration Testing
Penetration testing evaluates the system's resistance to known attack vectors relevant to the
threat model. MAC address spoofing tests verify that the blockchain-only lookup correctly
denies devices with spoofed MAC addresses not in the authorized registry, and that the AI
anomaly detector identifies the behavioral fingerprint of spoofing attacks through statistical
analysis. Replay attack tests against the blockchain REST API verify that the Flask server
correctly handles repeated identical requests without granting spurious authorizations.DDoS simulation using hping3 traffic generation verifies that the AI detector identifies
DDoS flow characteristics within 5-second detection windows and triggers automatic flow
blocking through the Ryu controller.CHAPTER 3: RESULTS AND DISCUSSION
3.1 Experimental Results
3.1.1 Authentication Performance
Authentication latency measurements were collected across 500 device authentication
events under three conditions: single device sequential authentication, 10 concurrent device
authentications, and 50 concurrent device authentications (simulating a full classroom
device activation scenario). Measurements encompass the complete authentication pipeline
from OpenFlow Packet-In generation through blockchain REST API query to flow rule
installation.
